                    <p class="text-center text-slate-600 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">AGI is not just a more powerful version of today's AI. It represents a categorical leap in capability, moving from task-specific skills to generalized, autonomous reasoning and learning.</p>
                    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
                        <table class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto text-left border-collapse">
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th class="border-b-2 border-slate-300 p-4 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 font-semibold">Capability</th>
