                                    <td class="p-4 border-b border-slate-200">Can generalize knowledge to solve completely new problems.</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr class="bg-slate-50">
                                    <td class="p-4 border-b border-slate-200 font-medium">Self-Improvement</td>
                                    <td class="p-4 border-b border-slate-200">Static architecture; does not modify its own code.</td>
                                    <td class="p-4 border-b border-slate-200">Recursive self-improvement, potentially leading to rapid intelligence explosion (ASI).</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
