                    <p class="text-center text-slate-600 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">The emergence of a superintelligence (ASI) that vastly exceeds human cognition presents the "Bostrom Problem": how do we ensure its goals are aligned with ours? This raises profound questions about control, instrumental convergence, and existential risk.</p>
                    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4 text-center">The Landscape of AGI Risks</h4>
                        <p class="text-center text-slate-600 mb-6">The risks posed by advanced AI are multi-faceted, extending beyond catastrophic scenarios to include profound societal, ethical, and economic disruptions. Effective governance must address this entire spectrum.</p>
