                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4 text-center">Supranational Trusteeship: A Global Approach</h3>
                    <p class="text-center text-slate-600 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Because AGI's impact will be global, its governance must transcend national borders. The book explores analogues from international law to propose a global trusteeship model.</p>
